{
  "stem": "14928.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I found [INAUDIBLE]-- I went over with a passport.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because they came every-- they came in every house to look for refugees.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I took a passport from a girl that I lived with, a niece from Ruthie Kramer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I took it with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I went to the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I went to the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I said that I want to go through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, I just didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So everybody was looking at me like crazy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If they don't bother you, why would you want to but yourself go?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And nobody even asked me for a passport.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know why, but nobody asked me for a passport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I had my-- have a passport in my pocket, but nobody asked me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The only thing they did is chase me away from the refugees.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said, you go away from here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You go away from here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You don't belong here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I went away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And what I knew-- I don't know how I let my uncle in Lubon.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I told you I had an aunt and uncle in Lubon, where we came first there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He probably knew by himself that they probably did, from Lubon, the same thing with the refugees.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he came with the horse and buggy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was a cripple from World War I, where they was-- he was-- he was walking on crutches.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had to come all night, sitting on that horse and buggy all night, to bring me my sister's passport.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because my sister-- middle sister used to go there to visit, for Pesach, for [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sukkot. ?] When I was in Lodz, she used to go there.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
